tory.\", \"from\": 281, \"to\": 320, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the third-fastest time\", \"from\": 286, \"to\": 308}, {\"ngram\": \"history\", \"from\": 312, \"to\": 319}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Olympic bronze medalist Katharine Berkoff earned silver Wednesday, touching the wall in 54.93.\", \"from\": 322, \"to\": 416, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 346, \"end\": 363, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Katharine_Berkoff\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Katharine Berkoff\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Katharine_Berkoff\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Katharine_Berkoff\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"silver\", \"from\": 371, \"to\": 377}, {\"ngram\": \"the wall\", \"from\": 398, \"to\": 406}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Smith, 22, previously won Olympic silver medals in the 100m and 200m backstrokes in Paris, plus world titles in the 100m back in 2022 and the 200m back in 2019 in a 50-meter pool.\", \"from\": 418, \"to\": 597, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 502, \"end\": 507, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999997426635094, \"rank\": 2.573365758381771e-07, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Smith\", \"from\": 418, \"to\": 423}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympic silver medals\", \"from\": 444, \"to\": 465}, {\"ngram\": \"the 100m\", \"from\": 469, \"to\": 477}, {\"ngram\": \"200m backstrokes\", \"from\": 482, \"to\": 498}, {\"ngram\": \"world titles\", \"from\": 514, \"to\": 526}, {\"ngram\": \"the 100m\", \"from\": 530, \"to\": 538}, {\"ngram\": \"the 200m\", \"from\": 556, \"to\": 564}, {\"ngram\": \"a 50-meter pool\", \"from\": 581, \"to\": 596}]}, {\"sentence\": \"SHORT COURSE WORLDS:Full Results|Broadcast Schedule Short course worlds are held in a 25-meter pool, unlike most major international meets.\", \"from\": 599, \"to\": 739, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"SHORT COURSE WORLDS\", \"from\": 599, \"to\": 618}, {\"ngram\": \"Schedule Short course worlds\", \"from\": 642, \"to\": 670}, {\"ngram\": \"a 25-meter pool\", \"from\": 683, \"to\": 698}, {\"ngram\": \"most major international meets\", \"from\": 707, \"to\": 737}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Smith has been busy since the Paris Games.\", \"from\": 741, \"to\": 783, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Smith\", \"from\": 741, \"to\": 746}, {\"ngram\": \"the Paris Games\", \"from\": 767, \"to\": 782}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She competed at all three legs of the World Aquatics World Cup series (also in short course pools) in October and November, breaking world records in the 100m and 200m backstrokes.\", \"from\": 784, \"to\": 964, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 837, \"end\": 846, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/FIS_Alpine_Ski_World_Cup\", \"score\": 0.9774981171128757, \"rank\": 0.022893841603532344, \"text\": \"World Cup\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/FIS_Alpine_Ski_World_Cup\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/FIS_Alpine_Ski_World_Cup\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"all three legs\", \"from\": 800, \"to\": 814}, {\"ngram\": \"short course pools\", \"from\": 863, \"to\": 881}, {\"ngram\": \"October\", \"from\": 886, \"to\": 893}, {\"ngram\": \"November\", \"from\": 898, \"to\": 906}, {\"ngram\": \"world records\", \"from\": 917, \"to\": 930}, {\"ngram\": \"the 100m\", \"from\": 934, \"to\": 942}, {\"ngram\": \"200m backstrokes\", \"from\": 947, \"to\": 963}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"All my coaches at ASU (Arizona State) and Texas have been great about letting me have a lot of patience this fall and training when I want to and have a lot of fun and flexibility with short course,\\\" she said.\", \"from\": 966, \"to\": 1176, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 985, \"end\": 988, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org